user.biography: 📚Author🍋 Lemon thief 🙄 creator 💋 whiskey purveyor 🥃 @doomswhiskey  ✨ please buy my book 👇🏻👇🏻 ✨ @adrenaline_pr for press inquiries ✨🤟

node.text: Here is a true story about me getting a tattoo. A short documentary film, by me. It will be on my body forever and I couldn’t be more happy about it. Thank you @beauxbrady 🔪 @portcitytattooca 🔪 (and thank you @jessiexlee for the referral) 🤟
